com.google.gcloud.bigquery

Class BaseTableInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gcloud.bigquery.BaseTableInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExternalTableInfo, TableInfo, ViewInfo

    public abstract class BaseTableInfo
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Base class for Google BigQuery table information. Use TableInfo for a simple BigQuery Table. Use ViewInfo for a BigQuery View Table. Use ExternalTableInfo for a BigQuery Table backed by external data.
    See Also:
    Managing Tables, Serialized Form

      • type

        public BaseTableInfo.Type type()
        Returns the table's type. If this table is simple table the method returns BaseTableInfo.Type.TABLE. If this table is an external table this method returns BaseTableInfo.Type.EXTERNAL. If this table is a view table this method returns BaseTableInfo.Type.VIEW.
